46:00.891 --> 46:03.883
No. I'm just
givin'you the facts.

46:03.961 --> 46:06.521
You can do
what you want with them.

46:12.903 --> 46:17.033
That Auggie,
he's gonna drive me crazy.

46:17.107 --> 46:21.703
Just when I get the deal together,
he comes in playin' those fuckin' violins.

46:22.713 --> 46:24.840
Brooklyn! Hmph.

46:26.116 --> 46:30.712
Brooklyn. I'm supposed
to care about Brooklyn.

46:30.788 --> 46:34.121
I don't even live in this
shit hole of a town anymore.

46:41.165 --> 46:44.066
Hiya, Vinny.

46:44.134 --> 46:46.602
Jackie!

46:46.670 --> 46:50.128
In the flesh, sport.

46:50.207 --> 46:54.667
Jackie, the greatest
ballplayer of them all.

46:54.745 --> 46:58.340
I used to pray for you
every night when I was a kid.

46:58.415 --> 47:02.044
I was the man
that changed America, Vinny.

47:02.119 --> 47:05.782
And I did it all right here,
in Brooklyn.

47:05.856 --> 47:09.155
Oh, they spat at me.
Cursed me.

47:09.226 --> 47:11.694
Made my life
a never-ending hell.

47:11.762 --> 47:14.128
And I wasn't allowed
to fight back.

47:16.300 --> 47:20.794
It takes its toll,
being a martyr.

47:20.871 --> 47:24.807
I died when I was
53 years old, Vinny.

47:24.875 --> 47:28.106
Even younger
than you are now.

47:28.178 --> 47:31.306
But I was a hell
of a ballplayer, wasn't I?

47:31.381 --> 47:35.112
The best, Jackie.
You were the best there was.

47:35.185 --> 47:37.676
Things changed after me.

47:37.754 --> 47:41.121
Not just for black people.
For white people too.

47:41.191 --> 47:45.184
After me, well, white people
and black people...

47:45.262 --> 47:49.699
never looked at each other
in the same old way anymore.

47:49.766 --> 47:53.600
And it all happened
right here, in Brooklyn.

47:55.038 --> 47:59.475
Yeah, then they...
moved the team away.

47:59.543 --> 48:03.377
Almost broke my heart. What'd they do
a dumb thing like that for?

48:03.447 --> 48:07.440
Dollars and cents,
Vinny.

48:07.517 --> 48:10.042
Ebbets Field
may be gone now...

48:10.120 --> 48:14.284
but what happened there
lives on in the mind.

48:14.358 --> 48:19.261
That's where it counts, Vinny.
Mind over matter.

48:19.329 --> 48:23.356
There are more important
things in life than baseball.

48:23.433 --> 48:27.426
But, Brooklyn looks good.

48:27.504 --> 48:31.338
More or less the same it was
the last time I saw it.

48:31.408 --> 48:34.571
And Prospect Park over there.

48:34.645 --> 48:37.739
Still as beautiful as ever.

48:39.683 --> 48:45.417
Say, Vinny, they don't still
make those Belgian waffles, do they?

48:45.489 --> 48:50.984
Ah, man! What I wouldn't give to sink
my teeth into a Belgian waffle!

48:51.061 --> 48:55.054
Two scoops of pistachio ice cream,
