48:55.132 --> 48:58.727
Hmph. Boy,
do I miss those things.

48:58.802 --> 49:02.761
Belgian waffles, sure.
They still make 'em.

49:02.839 --> 49:06.434
Just go down two blocks
to the Cosmic Diner.

49:06.510 --> 49:10.276
Jackie, they'll make you
all the Belgian waffles you want.

49:10.347 --> 49:13.316
Thanks, sport.

49:13.383 --> 49:16.352
Don't mind if I do.

49:16.420 --> 49:20.720
A day in Brooklyn just wouldn't be complete
without stopping in for a Belgian waffle.

49:20.791 --> 49:22.759
Would it?

49:26.997 --> 49:30.700
Every day 7,999...

49:30.767 --> 49:35.295
Belgian waffles are eaten
in the restaurants of Brooklyn.

